file: tmp_【＃百鬼あやめ４周年記念 ⧸ 3DLIVE】Nakiriayame 4th anniversary　~Hapiness to you ♡~ [mwJGZ8YU7o4]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_008.mov

scenes.description: The MC section following the performance of "Tsubaki," featuring Nakiri Ayame, Ookami Mio, and Shirakami Fubuki. They discuss the difficulty of the choreography and introduce the 3D DJ mascot, Poyoyo.
A short blackout transition between scenes.
Performance of the song "Daishikyu Daishuki" by Nakiri Ayame and Sakamata Chloe.

subtitles.original: 楽しかったー！
subtitles.english: That was fun!

subtitles.original: 楽しかったね。
subtitles.english: It really was.

subtitles.original: こうやって3人で「せーの」っていうことがあまりなかったから…
subtitles.english: Since we rarely get to say "one, two!" together like this...

subtitles.original: 確かに。
subtitles.english: True.

subtitles.original: 新鮮だった。
subtitles.english: It felt fresh.

subtitles.original: 新鮮ですね。
subtitles.english: It really does.

subtitles.original: ねー。
subtitles.english: Right?

subtitles.original: 改めてまして。
subtitles.english: Once again...

subtitles.original: 改めてまして、よろしくお願いします！
subtitles.english: Once again, it's a pleasure to be here!

subtitles.original: 先ほども呼んでいただいたんですけれども。
subtitles.english: We were called up earlier as well.

subtitles.original: そうね。
subtitles.english: That's right.

subtitles.original: 2回目！よかったー！
subtitles.english: A second time! I'm so glad!

subtitles.original: ありがとうございます！
subtitles.english: Thank you so much!

subtitles.original: 歌い上がってしまって、ハッハハってなっちゃったね。
subtitles.english: We got so into the singing, we were all like, "Ha-ha-ha!"

subtitles.original: えー、3人では「恋情詩歌」と…
subtitles.english: So, as a trio, we sang "Renjo Shika" and...

subtitles.original: ね、「ツバキ」を。
subtitles.english: ...right, "Tsubaki."

subtitles.original: 歌いましたけども、「ツバキ」がね、なんと！
subtitles.english: We sang them, and "Tsubaki" was actually...

subtitles.original: ここ、YouTubeでは初！
subtitles.english: ...performed here on YouTube for the first time!

subtitles.original: 初お披露目ということで！
subtitles.english: It was the first public performance!

subtitles.original: 嬉しいー！
subtitles.english: I'm so happy!

subtitles.original: そうだよ！やっとだよ！
subtitles.english: Exactly! Finally!

subtitles.original: ね、初めて見る人間様もいるんじゃないですか？
subtitles.english: I bet there are humans seeing it for the first time, right?

subtitles.original: 絶対いるね。
subtitles.english: Definitely.

subtitles.original: ねー。そう。どうだったかな？
subtitles.english: Yeah. So, how was it?

subtitles.original: どうでした？どうでした？コメント欄で教えてくださいね。
subtitles.english: What did you think? Let us know in the comments.

subtitles.original: これ、難しいんだよね、意外と。
subtitles.english: This is surprisingly difficult, you know.

subtitles.original: 「恋情詩歌」も、 mecha 難しいんだよね。
subtitles.english: "Renjo Shika" is also super difficult.

subtitles.original: 一生懸命頑張って、間違ってないといいんですけども。
subtitles.english: We tried our best, so I hope we didn't make any mistakes.

subtitles.original: いいとこだけ見てください。
subtitles.english: Please only pay attention to the good parts.

subtitles.original: 間違ってるなと思ったら、ちょっと見なかったことで。忘れてください。
subtitles.english: If you think we messed up, just pretend you didn't see it. Please forget it.

subtitles.original: いいとこだけ、お願いします！
subtitles.english: Only the good parts, please!

subtitles.original: そして、なんか今日後ろに…
subtitles.english: And also, there's something behind us today...

subtitles.original: そうなんですよ！見て！
subtitles.english: That's right! Look!

subtitles.original: 4周年記念で、ぽよよん実装！
subtitles.english: For the 4th anniversary, Poyoyo is here!

subtitles.original: うわー！すごい！
subtitles.english: Whoa! Amazing!

subtitles.original: めっちゃ動いてるよ。
subtitles.english: It's moving so much.

subtitles.original: DJぽよよ。すごーい！揺れとる揺れとる。
subtitles.english: DJ Poyoyo. Incredible! It's swaying!

subtitles.original: なんかさ、このぽよよさ、リハではなんかもうちょっと違ったんだよね。
subtitles.english: You know, this Poyoyo was a bit different in rehearsal.

subtitles.original: そうなんですよ。確かに。
subtitles.english: That's true. Indeed.

subtitles.original: 実はね、リハーサルではサングラスかけてて。
subtitles.english: Actually, it was wearing sunglasses in rehearsal.

subtitles.original: ああ、これ！これかけててね。
subtitles.english: Ah, these! It was wearing these.

subtitles.original: サングラスも…あ！動くんだよ、動く！
subtitles.english: The sunglasses also—oh! They move, they move!

subtitles.original: やばい、もう。これ、本番なくしたよね、リハで見て。
subtitles.english: Oh my god. We decided to remove them for the show after seeing them in rehearsal.

subtitles.original: そうなんだよね、あまりにも存在感が…
subtitles.english: Yeah, its presence was just so...

subtitles.original: 大きすぎて。確かに。
subtitles.english: ...overwhelming. Definitely.

subtitles.original: 踊ってる最中、後ろでずっとさ、カメラに絶対入るぽよよ、みたいなって。
subtitles.english: While we were dancing, Poyoyo was back there, definitely getting into the shot.

subtitles.original: 完全体ぽよ。笑ってできないっていう。
subtitles.english: Perfect form Poyoyo. We couldn't stop laughing and keep performing.

subtitles.original: 笑ってできなくなっちゃったので、本番ではね、ちょっと外していただきました。
subtitles.english: Since we couldn't help laughing, we had them removed for the actual performance.

subtitles.original: チラチラ、チラチラ。可愛いけども。
subtitles.english: Glancing back at it. It's cute, though.

subtitles.original: めっちゃ可愛いけどねー。
subtitles.english: It really is super cute.

subtitles.original: じゃあ、これから、ちょっとこの後どうする？焼肉でも食べに行く？
subtitles.english: Well then, what should we do after this? Go eat some yakiniku?

subtitles.original: 行きたい、行きたい！踊ったし、お腹空いちゃった。
subtitles.english: I want to go! We danced, and now I'm hungry.

subtitles.original: あやめは？行きたいんだけど、まだこの後もあるんです。
subtitles.english: What about you, Ayame? I want to go, but I still have more to do after this.

subtitles.original: この後もあるの！？そう、この後も。
subtitles.english: There's more?! Yes, more after this.

subtitles.original: じゃあ、この後もうちらで見守ってようか。いいね、見守ってよう。
subtitles.english: In that case, let's keep watching over you. Sounds good, let's watch.

subtitles.original: じゃあ、ちょっと二人に見守ってもらおうかな。
subtitles.english: Then, I guess I'll have you two watch over me.

subtitles.original: 見守ってるぜ。頑張るよ、ありがとう！
subtitles.english: We're watching. I'll do my best, thank you!

subtitles.original: じゃあ、あっちで見守っとくか。行こっか。
subtitles.english: Alright, let's head over there and watch. Let's go.

subtitles.original: 行ってきまーす。ありがとうね、頑張ってね！
subtitles.english: Off we go. Thanks for having us, good luck!

subtitles.original: 頑張るよー！バイバーイ！
subtitles.english: I'll do my best! Bye-bye!
